OL,3,COlympian admits to cheating on ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend shorty after winning bronze
OL,5,Cmedal
OL,7,FA Norwegian Olympian who confessed to
OL,8,Fcheating on his ex-girlfriend after
OL,9,Fwinning a bronze medal on Tuesday has
OL,10,Fsaid he hopes "she will see what she
OL,11,Freally means to me".
OL,13,FSpeaking at a media briefing shortly
OL,14,Fafter finishing third in the 20-
OL,15,Fkilometre individual biathlon at the
OL,16,FWinter Olympics, Sturla Holm Laegreid
OL,17,Fsaid: "I don't want to think I didn't
OL,18,Ftry everything to get her back."
