OL,7,FFor Laegreid, the bronze medal in the
OL,8,Fevent (which combines skiing and
OL,9,Fshooting) did not quite compare to the
OL,10,F"gold medal" he had lost in his ex-
OL,11,Fgirlfriend.
OL,13,FIn a post-race interview immediately
OL,14,Fafter the finish, the seven-time world
OL,15,Fchampion told Norwegian broadcaster
OL,16,FNRK: "Six months ago, I met the love
OL,17,Fof my life and the most beautiful and
OL,18,Fkindest person in the world.
OL,20,F"And three months ago I made my
OL,21,Fbiggest mistake and cheated on her."
