OL,7,FThe 28-year-old confessed at the media
OL,8,Fbriefing that he does not know if he
OL,9,Fmade the right choice in announcing
OL,10,Fhis feelings to the world.
OL,12,FHe told journalists: "Yeah, really I
OL,13,Fdon't know if it's the right choice or
OL,14,Fnot, but it was the choice I made. We
OL,15,Fmake different choices during our
OL,16,Flife, and that's how you make life,
OL,17,Fbasically.
