OL,5,Cmedal
OL,7,F"So today I made the choice to tell
OL,8,Fthe world what I did, so maybe there
OL,9,Fis a chance that she will see what she
OL,10,Freally means to me. And maybe not."
OL,12,FHis ex-girlfriend, who remains
OL,13,Fanonymous, has now reportedly
OL,14,Fresponded.
OL,16,FWriting to Norwegian newspaper VG, she
OL,17,Fsaid: "It's hard to forgive. Even
OL,18,Fafter a declaration of love in front
OL,19,Fof the whole world."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
