OL,7,FShe continued: "I did not choose to be
OL,8,Fput in this position, and it hurts to
OL,9,Fhave to be in it. We have had contact
OL,10,Fand he is aware of my opinions on
OL,11,Fthis."
OL,13,FLaegreid's success on Tuesday earned
OL,14,Fhim his first individual Olympic
OL,15,Fmedal, having previously won gold in
OL,16,Fthe relay at the 2022 Beijing Olympics.
OL,18,FHe finished behind the French athlete
OL,19,FEric Perrot, and his teammate Johan-
OL,20,FOlav Botn who won gold in his Olympic
OL,21,Fdebut.
